💰 Tip Calculator

A simple Tip Calculator App built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
This project allows users to quickly calculate the tip amount and the total bill based on a given percentage.

🚀 Features

Input bill amount

Input tip percentage

Instantly calculate:

✅ Tip amount 💵

✅ Total amount (bill + tip)

User-friendly design with clean UI

Real-time calculation with formatted output

🛠️ Technologies Used

HTML5 – Structure of the app

CSS3 – Styling and layout

JavaScript (Vanilla JS) – Core functionality & DOM manipulation

📂 Project Structure
📁 Tip-Calculator
 ┣ 📜 index.html      # Main HTML file
 ┣ 📜 style.css       # Styling
 ┣ 📜 scripts.js      # JavaScript logic
 ┗ 📜 README.md       # Project documentation

💻 How to Use

Clone this repository:

git clone https://github.com/your-username/tip-calculator.git


Open index.html in your browser.

Enter your bill amount and tip percentage.

Click CALCULATE to see the results.

